began in Atlanta on Tuesday with ``Grammy in the Schools,'' a
day-long conference designed to educate Atlanta-area students about
how to pursue a career in the music business. Local NARAS members,
who are now voting on awards, met with kids in a day of workshops
at the Rialto Center _ and shared their thoughts about the upcoming
awards show in Los Angeles. (Longino, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 12-15. WITH PHOTO.
