<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-26 13:58 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8902 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SOC-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      01-26 1100
