<HEADLINE>
EDITORS: A MERE WEEK AFTER HIS RETURN TO JORDAN FOLLOWING SIX
MONTHS OF CANCER TREATMENT IN AMERICA, KING HUSSEIN IS BEING RUSHED
BACK TO THE MAYO CLINIC AS YOU READ THIS. WE ARE PLEASED TO OFFER
YOU THE FOLLOWING EXCELLENT STORY _ FULL OF INSIGHT, PALACE
INTRIGUE AND POIGNANCY _ ON THE ALMOST SHAKESPEAREAN RETURN, AND
DEPARTURE AGAIN, OF KING HUSSEIN.)  
 
</HEADLINE>
   (This compelling ``separate buy'' article is from the Independent
of London, distributed by the New York Times Syndicate.)  
  
 (To publish this article, it must be purchased from the New York
