<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-26 17:20 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9281 &Cx1f; taf-z
u d &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NAPA-BRANDY-3TAKES-NY     01-26 0986
