of Wednesday, Jan. 27. If you have any questions, call the Cox News
Service desk in Atlanta at 800-950-3739 or 404-526-5456. We are
staffed 8 a.m. to 10 p.m. Monday-Friday, and 1-10 p.m. on weekends.
