time in its 33-year history, the Super Bowl will be played while an
impeached American president is on trial in the U.S. Senate. You
may think this is coincidental. You may even imagine that the two
events, each of them grand spectacles on the American stage, have
no connections or similarities. But you probably haven't given this
as much thought as I have. If you did, you'd see that the
connection between these two pageants might seem tenuous at first.
But not when you take a deeper look. (Cerrabino, Palm Beach Post)
