   WITH: AT A GLANCE -- A look at the Ford Ranger. (DeVault,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   WITH: THE MECHANIC -- As automotive electrical systems become
more complex and computer-dependent, the once relatively simple
role of the battery takes on a whole new dimension. (Carter,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   TECHNOLOGY
</P>
<P>
   TELECOM-MECCA _ ATLANTA _ While no one was paying attention, the
non-descript, 1950s building at 55 Marietta St. has become a kind
of Mecca for aspiring telecommunications companies. At last count,
32 companies _ including Qwest, Allegiance and Teligent _ have
switching equipment in the building .... what's up with that?
(Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
