Association's greatest sideman might have an opportunity to command
a more prominent part of the stage, but Scottie Pippen said he is
satisfied to blend in with the Houston Rockets, just as he did for
most of his 11 years in Chicago. (Rosner, Austin
American-Statesman) MOVED.
