   FBN-ELWAY-REEVES _ John Elway ran Dan Reeves out of Denver. All
Reeves did while he was there was coach Elway and the Broncos to
four Super Bowls. What's behind the sour relationship between the
two and what is current Denver coach Mike Shanahan's role in it?
(Woods, Palm Beach Post).
</P>
<P>
   FBN-MORTANDERSEN _ Morten Andersen has been a stellar kicker in
the NFL for a long time. But until he made the overtime field goal
that got the Atlanta Falcons into their first Super Bowl, he was
best known for blowing an easy kick in 1996 that allowed the
Jacksonville Jaguars to make the playoffs for the first time.
(Skolnick, Palm Beach Post).
</P>
