</P>
<P>
   P&AMP;G-AD-COLUMN _ The Procter &AMP; Gamble Co., the world's largest
advertiser, is reducing its agency roster again in a paring that
ends a relationship with one shop dating back 43 years. By Stuart
Elliott.
</P>
<P>
   (Scheduled to move by 9 p.m. ET.)
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
