INTERNET-AUCTION (Los Angeles) _ Going once, going twice, going
crazy. That's the story of auction sites on the Internet, such as
giant eBay, where you can unload your junk to a hungry nation of
millions looking for collectibles, antiques, computer bargains and
more. The auction sites are one of the fastest-growing niches on
the `Net, with lots of money to be made. By David Bloom. 
. 

