<HEADLINE>
EDITORS: A MERE WEEK AFTER HIS RETURN TO JORDAN FOLLOWING SIX
MONTHS OF CANCER TREATMENT IN AMERICA, KING HUSSEIN WAS RUSHED BACK
TO THE MAYO CLINIC TUESDAY. WE ARE PLEASED TO OFFER YOU THE
FOLLOWING EXCELLENT STORY _ FULL OF INSIGHT, PALACE INTRIGUE AND
POIGNANCY _ ON THE ALMOST SHAKESPEAREAN RETURN, AND DEPARTURE
AGAIN, OF KING HUSSEIN.)  
 
</HEADLINE>
